{"tid":1099850,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"華納起訴白宮 指控Trump競選廣告未經授權使用Hans Zimmer 蝙蝠俠配樂","createTime":"2019-04-10T04:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T23:41:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f79198ebfd8024d76df38773cb727ead959471c3","tid":1099850,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sRCWsaq3XBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsRCWsaq3XBQ&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhImWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=08143c74\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sRCWsaq3XBQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華納將起訴白宮，狀告美國總統特朗普在他的競選視頻中使用《夜神起義》的音樂涉嫌侵權。華納確認將提告，並發布聲明：&ldquo;在競選視頻中使用華納兄弟的音樂是未經授權的，我們致力通過正當法律渠道將其移除。&rdquo;特朗普已把該視頻發布推特，華納的訴狀中，將要求他把該視頻從推特賬號刪除。視頻中使用了漢斯&middot;季默的《Why Do We Fall?》，並且使用了電影的標題字體。"},{"pid":"1e327a450ef945071cf61886a0d3c717ba74da50","tid":1099850,"uid":3747,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:06:57.000Z","msg":"DC又贏"},{"pid":"d2b50dbc18094ef55c2d6e4fa3cf955a03cf5c29","tid":1099850,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"DC小氣到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640c60248ccc85cf4afee8bbfe08d2b7f6758c06","tid":1099850,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"好撚正<br />\nHe's the hero Gotham deserves, but not the one it needs right now."},{"pid":"376f07aff944b5fff9d55aad8a6ebfd0dacc35e5","tid":1099850,"uid":236359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"粵劇Trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d41ace4ff720e3d572d86a04c6ab9214501a4","tid":1099850,"uid":123264,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"白撚痴<br />\n條片又唔係佢official整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo